ginzDecFormat(double, int, int) - Static method in class com.techelevator.ginzUtilities
Returns a String presentation of the double value passed (1st argument) with the total number of digits (2nd argurment) and the number of decimal places requested (3rd argument) The value will be rounded to the number of decimal places passed when creating the return value
